{"tid":1530793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好消息！我地就快贏！香港人好快有真普選","createTime":"2019-09-02T05:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:59:43.000Z","uid":278380,"like":16,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7a9bc26c8e03821d8615c6d63e4b590802b633b","tid":1530793,"uid":278380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我贏你老母咩<br />\n你地自問做過d咩啊？<br />\n憑咩有民主<br />\n有無努力爭取過啊？<br />\n盡左力未啊？<br />\n三罷？ 我吥 身邊本身大部份黃底<br />\n但今日返工既朋友仲多過罷工！<br />\n藍絲望住我地呢班曱甴真係笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷工仲要希望係被罷工<br />\n連累搞不合作運動既年輕人俾人拉埋！<br />\n你地開心啦宜家？！<br />\n返學罷課既學生又俾人搞<br />\n我真係笑出聲<br />\n係網絡上就大大聲話搞人<br />\n事實上就係俾人搞<br />\n6月至今有幾多人俾人拉左？！<br />\n你地就係度心情好先幫下手<br />\n我屌你老母咩<br />\n一齊準備打傻仔針啦香港人<br />\n對家就一直升級行動<br />\n愈做愈過火<br />\n我地呢？繼續齋嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無野好講了 無氣</span></span><br />\n最後一句 <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 垃圾</span></span>"},{"pid":"b4b67407640327f17e4b6a92fb173a5196fc28bf","tid":1530793,"uid":278380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"推比垃圾人睇"},{"pid":"f0c45f4ab2a081a2001d917666a08edc9cdbf744","tid":1530793,"uid":278380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"推比垃圾人睇"},{"pid":"7b70bd6642af2fd5fa845cf33a008c67364dac03","tid":1530793,"uid":278380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:05:40.000Z","msg":"推比垃圾人睇"},{"pid":"1a8daef04dac75c7863ed666c796441523ec5ca8","tid":1530793,"uid":278380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"推比垃圾人睇"},{"pid":"9ecba7aa81feafdff37905f78147204a364aa782","tid":1530793,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cla